<h2>Wood Interior</h2>
For a roof lantern with a wood interior, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> provides options of solid Mahogany or Spanish Cedar and laminates of¬†Western Red Cedar, Southern Yellow Pine, Douglas Fir, and Northern White Pine (straight eave applications only). Redwood and Cherry can also be integrated into your structure, depending on the final engineering requirements. Decorative finials, cresting, gutters, pediments, grids, and transoms can all be added to the roof lanterns‚Äô design to meet the creative tastes of each customer.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]
<h2><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37866" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/roof-lantern-skylight-decorative.png" alt="" width="680" height="400" /></h2>
<h2>Decorative Additions</h2>
